    "name": "诅咒之牌",
    "steam_appid": 2159900,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/42ec8d662c99faf491cb1b8d7704af23.poster.avif?t=1761062256\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/42ec8d662c99faf491cb1b8d7704af23.webm?t=1761062256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>诅咒之牌</strong>》是一款卡牌模拟形式的策略肉鸽自走棋游戏。你将浴火重生，重建城堡，踏上征程，再次让黑暗笼罩大地。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多个吸血鬼职业</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索强大的职业，每个职业的玩法各不相同。驯服怪物，调配药水，制作魔法武器，抢占上风。围绕你的不死军团制定策略。你的随从会是行动缓慢、坚不可摧的重甲单位，还是迅捷灵巧的轻甲战士？不同的构筑会产生不同的联动效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/98e107c00123e2bd2c0cd11cd0f1d13d.poster.avif?t=1761062256\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/98e107c00123e2bd2c0cd11cd0f1d13d.webm?t=1761062256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索大地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游走在不断变化的世界，隐藏的村庄和王国等待你去攻打。每个地方都有新的资源等你发现，也有不同的敌人需要面对。还有云游商人、强盗打劫和暴风雪等随机事件，让每一次游戏体验都新鲜、刺激。除此之外，各地散落着神秘的神器。完成特殊的挑战，就能知道它们的位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/36e339e282c86cc7ef310ffdb1cc37cf.poster.avif?t=1761062256\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/36e339e282c86cc7ef310ffdb1cc37cf.webm?t=1761062256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重建城堡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的城堡已成废墟。只有你能让它重现辉煌！沙盒模式可以让你垒起高墙、塔楼、大门和装饰，建起属于自己的城堡，解锁持久的加成和强大的升级项目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/6b2ae9cc5f29153481b568498e079ba1.poster.avif?t=1761062256\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/6b2ae9cc5f29153481b568498e079ba1.webm?t=1761062256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/6b2ae9cc5f29153481b568498e079ba1.mp4?t=1761062256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的道路</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索武器和装备的海量强大效果，塑造自己独有的玩法风格。尝试不同的搭配，摸索精彩刺激的联动效果，让每场战斗都惊心动魄而又成就满满。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/ace3f65774b4852beda658d930266766.poster.avif?t=1761062256\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/ace3f65774b4852beda658d930266766.webm?t=1761062256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159900/extras/ace3f65774b4852beda658d930266766.mp4?t=1761062256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
